17
00:04:01,121 --> 00:04:03,468
Ale aj tak mám každú noc nočné mory...

18
00:04:05,674 --> 00:04:08,260
...sníva sa mi, že ten muž ide ku mne...

19
00:04:09,906 --> 00:04:12,270
Nech sa snažím akokoľvek schovať,

20
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:16,500
stále ma prenasleduje.

21
00:04:20,045 --> 00:04:22,400
Tak ho zabijem.

22
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,500
V mojich snoch,

23
00:04:27,651 --> 00:04:29,650
